headline: Tim Rausch joins Ameren board of directors
summary: Ameren Corporation (NYSE: AEE) announced today that Timothy S. Rausch has been elected to the Ameren board of directors, effective March 1.

headline: American Electric Power to Post Q4 Earnings: What's in Store?
